<plot>A riotous dark comedy that chronicles the morose tale of Binky the Mime, who is tried for having mimed the murder of an innocent passerby one random fateful evening. When a mime's silence will no longer be heard, the innocent shall suffer. Witness the story of a poor soul trapped in a world that doesn't exist. A silent web of violence spun by a man scorned, pushed over the edge. A man trapped by the system, condemned by society, and generally hated by clowns. His message is a desperate cry to the world for attention. This is the story of Binky the mime, who was put to trial for murder - for MIMING a murder.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?370346</url></doc>
